attributes.Long form description: The instructor says, please assemble this chair. The student assembles the legs, then she assembles the seat; after, she screws the first, the second, the third, and the fourth screw. Finally she tightens the middle hex nut.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, welcome, and thank you for taking part in our study. In front of you, you will see the parts needed to assemble a stool from IKEA.
Your task, for now, will please assemble it. You may now begin.
